Name: CData Software, Inc.
Description: CData Software is a leading provider of data access and connectivity solutions. CData technologies extend the real-time data connectivity capabilities of SAS Products, providing live connectivity to more than 150+ Enterprise data sources that flow through existing SAS/Access methods.
